TITLE:: NxRange
summary:: A NexusUI range slider widget
categories:: NexusUI
related:: Classes/NxWidget

DESCRIPTION::
A NexusUI range slider widget - http://www.nexusosc.com/api/#range

CLASSMETHODS::


INSTANCEMETHODS::

METHOD:: stop

returns:: where the range stops.

METHOD:: start

returns:: where the range starts.

METHOD:: size

returns:: how big the range is.


EXAMPLES::

code::
(
r = NxRange();
r.action = { |nx| [nx.start, nx.stop, nx.size].postln }
)

r.start = 0.4;
r.stop = 0.6;
::
